&lt;li&gt;You have first-class SQL skills and 3+ years of experience in a relevant role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You understand the importance of data modeling, like knowing your Kimballs, your star schemas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You value business context and improvement as much as you do first-class technical solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You love collaboration and take pride in working in high-functioning teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You enjoy working in rapidly evolving, hyper-growth environments where every change presents an opportunity for us to grow&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You love having fun at work. Ping Pong/Mario Kart skills are a plus!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Scopely, we create games for everyone - and want to ensure that the people behind our games reflect that! &amp;nbsp; We are committed to creating a diverse, supportive work environment where everyone is treated with respect. We are committed to providing equal employment opportunities and welcome individuals from all backgrounds to join us &amp;amp; embrace the adventure!&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
