&lt;p&gt;Scopely is looking for a&amp;nbsp;DEI Program Operations Specialist&amp;nbsp;to join our Diversity, Equity and Inclusion team within the People function, in Barcelona working on a hybrid basis from the hub.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
