&lt;p&gt;We make sure our teams have everything they need to create amazing games. The People team manages everything from benefits &amp;amp; employee engagement to professional development opportunities and more!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
