&lt;li&gt;Lead the Monster Hunter Now marketing team by demonstrating in-depth knowledge of mobile game/app marketing tactics, user acquisition, engagement and retention, as well as effective general marketing practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Together with the team, solidify product positioning, author key messaging, and help develop marketing campaigns.&lt;/li&gt;
