&lt;li&gt;Experience working on a highly cross-functional with the ability to coordinate dynamic projects with internal and external partners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Outstanding verbal and written communication skills in English and Japanese, with experience in developing and delivering executive-level presentations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep understanding and passion for Niantic’s mission and values.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work in a fast-paced hybrid environment. Handle stress appropriately. Solve practical problems and adapt to dynamic situations with little notice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
